{"tid":1160653,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"謝拉畢拿同曉治積曼都幾相似，不過星途落後少少","createTime":"2019-05-18T15:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T15:58:56.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44d9cabdd2ac3da34f6300031a5577ea494f4a7c","tid":1160653,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完《白宮淪陷3》預告，再睇謝拉畢拿既資料就覺得佢同曉治積曼幾相似，首先都係外表好MAN既粗擴型男，年紀又接近（謝：49、曉：50），大家既戲路都係拍動作片得，需要演技既劇情片亦得（曉拍過《大娛樂家》，謝都拍過2014版《歌聲魅影》 ），但謝拉畢拿既知名度始終無做過狼人既曉治積曼咁高，拍既戲大部份都係B級片。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XF8h3hOGBJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXF8h3hOGBJM&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=585e7397\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XF8h3hOGBJM</a>"},{"pid":"69c9becb6a4debb2bf446c899b12d21efc132d56","tid":1160653,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"更正：謝都拍過<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2004版</span></strong>《歌聲魅影》"},{"pid":"a30a71c08d50347a277b4f8d0fa3e07a9aa0ff08","tid":1160653,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c8.alamy.com/comp/BPN2F3/gerard-butler-the-phantom-of-the-opera-2004-BPN2F3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc8.alamy.com%2Fcomp%2FBPN2F3%2Fgerard-butler-the-phantom-of-the-opera-2004-BPN2F3.jpg&h=f1ea33ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d9c8bec7f40028619831800e37ecfd21532797b","tid":1160653,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f15f8bd75911c3b85db71488fc11c7fe2dde8c7a","tid":1160653,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d9c8bec7f40028619831800e37ecfd21532797b","tid":1160653,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪